{"tid":191430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4月8日之潛水:用2分鐘睇晒各地新聞","createTime":"2017-04-08T01:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T01:23:43.000Z","uid":68591,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e775beb672530939da688b3be9a83fa742f4826e","tid":191430,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T01:01:25.000Z","msg":"早晨! 聽日開始行開1星期,唔好意思,我地1星期後見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每條新聞下面既link係新聞既sources,大家想進1步了解既可以入去條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港聞:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 特首辦宣佈特首梁振英本月中將率領多名司局長、行政會議成員，以及兩個發展委員會的委員，北上3日考察粵港澳大灣區的6大城市，包括廣州、肇慶等，了解各市規劃及創科發展。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00002/1491588654250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00002%2F1491588654250&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=e770371e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00002%2F1491588654250&h=f1e7d19e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00002/1491588654250</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170408/00176_031.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170408%2F00176_031.html&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=c57515bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170408/00176_031.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 民主黨、公民黨以及專業議政等泛民黨派證實接到候任特首辦邀請，預料最快4月下旬與林鄭月娥會面，但自決派等多名議員，包括面對議席資格司法覆核的羅冠聰、劉小麗等則尚未收到邀請。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00002/1491588644875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00002%2F1491588644875&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=3d5e49da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00002%2F1491588644875&h=d1c85134\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00002/1491588644875</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1578279&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1578279%26target%3D2&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=cbed3cc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1578279%26target%3D2&h=038e0b58\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1578279&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 無國界記者組織秘書長Christophe Deloire透露原打算將亞洲區首個辦事處落戶香港，但有感本港的法例未能保障他們，而且有被監視的可能，故宣佈改為在台北設置。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00002/1491588658369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00002%2F1491588658369&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d014b04d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00002%2F1491588658369&h=c7b35d15\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00002/1491588658369</a> (明報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 深圳市教育局近日發出通知，新學年公營學校可招收港澳籍學生，即使違反計劃生育政策下出生的學生都可以入學。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00002/1491588652815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00002%2F1491588652815&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=4219af50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00002%2F1491588652815&h=f1f29130\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00002/1491588652815</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170408/00176_020.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170408%2F00176_020.html&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=e6d30f19\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170408/00176_020.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 土地及建設諮詢委員會通過一項建橋建議，其容許以免補地價方式於來往中信大廈及金鐘廊的行人天橋加設一個駁口，以便建造另一條橫跨金鐘道的新橋，直接駁入太古廣場。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00002/1491588651208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00002%2F1491588651208&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=aa7f248e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00002%2F1491588651208&h=ae8b59a6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00002/1491588651208</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1578291&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1578291%26target%3D2&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a01d73f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1578291%26target%3D2&h=92168db5\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1578291&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 九龍醫院精神科病房一名患輕度弱智的男病人疑遭另一患精神分裂的病友摸臀非禮，該院醫護人員接獲當事人投訴後報警，案件交由九龍城警區刑事調查隊跟進。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00002/1491588650038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00002%2F1491588650038&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=db9d15b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00002%2F1491588650038&h=029489c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00002/1491588650038</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170408/00176_043.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170408%2F00176_043.html&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=28345fa3\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170408/00176_043.html</a> (東方日報)"},{"pid":"fa7882e4c86fbf8aff146ed6c912869594e16c8b","tid":191430,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T01:01:40.000Z","msg":"兩岸:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 訪美的國家主席習近平與美國總統特朗普在佛羅里達棕櫚灘的海湖莊園（Mar-a-Lago）會面，特朗普形容中美關係取得重大進展，他又接受習近平的訪華邀請。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00013/1491588677994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00013%2F1491588677994&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ca68846d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00013%2F1491588677994&h=9acf7052\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00013/1491588677994</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170408/00180_001.html\"