content.php?id=1578267&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 北京大學匯豐商學院與英國開放大學簽約，據報以880萬英鎊買下其位於英國牛津郡的莊園別墅校舍，並將於明年年初開設分校區。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170408/00178_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170408%2F00178_001.html&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=08b72042\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170408/00178_001.html</a> (東方日報)"},{"pid":"0c2806d19fc9dbc5db20aaf7ea3c05841261c7b8","tid":191430,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T01:01:50.000Z","msg":"國際:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 美國總統特朗普以懲罰發動「化武襲擊」的敘利亞巴沙爾政府為名，下令駐地中海的戰艦發射59枚「戰斧」巡航導彈襲擊駐有俄軍的一個敘空軍基地，據報只有23枚擊中目標，部分導彈擊中鄰近村莊，造成平民9死7傷。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00014/1491588685497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00014%2F1491588685497&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6b3932da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170408%2Fs00014%2F1491588685497&h=9b75c583\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170408/s00014/1491588685497</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170408/00180_014.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170408%2F00180_014.html&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2f3bd6fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170408/00180_014.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1578276&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fn